### 2. Global Reset Implementation 🏆
- **Functionality**: "Reset All Data" now performs a complete factory reset.
- **Scope**:
    - Clears **ALL** habit history.
    - Resets theme to default (Pastel).
    - **IMPORTANT**: Clears "Perfect Day" count (Stats page will reset to 0).
    - Clears all local storage data.
- **Verification**: Verified code implementation in [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/App.jsx) and [Profile.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/Profile.jsx).

